{"type":"message","id":"b5805b23","parentId":"40001097","timestamp":"2026-03-20T12:29:29.898Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Fri 2026-03-20 20:29 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 【第10轮 · 最终】尚书省与中书省已辩论9轮。尚书省坚持\"信息收集是执行阶段，零容错需要信息前置布局+精密研判\"。中书省坚持\"决策者有全局视野，应由中书统筹规划再交尚书执行\"。请两省分别发表最终陈词，简洁有力，3-5句话。格式：部门 + 最终陈词。"}],"timestamp":1774009769894}}
{"type":"message","id":"896d1410","parentId":"b5805b23","timestamp":"2026-03-20T12:29:45.742Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The task is clear - I need to write final statements (最终陈词) from both 尚书省 and 中书省 for the 10th and final round of their debate. Each should be 3-5 sentences, concise and powerful. The format should be \"部门 + 最终陈词\".\n\nLet me craft both statements:\n\n尚书省 (Shangshu Province) - insists information gathering is part of execution, zero-tolerance requires pre-positioning of information + precise analysis.\n\n中书省 (Zhongshu Province) - insists decision-makers have overall vision, should be Zhongshu统筹 planning then handed to Shangshu for execution.\n\n\nNow I'm writing out the final statements from both sides, each articulating their core position on how information and decision-making should be structured.","thinkingSignature":"dc5df2c639e9ad73b9e1a29b7f005c529b85c48cac30325b61d28625995a1c81"},{"type":"text","text":"**尚书省 · 最终陈词：**\n\n九轮激辩，核心未变：零容错的关键从来不是谁看得远，而是谁离战场最近。尚书省扎根执行前线，每日与真实信息流直接碰撞——任何宏图伟略，交给不了解现场细节的人去布局，都是把命运系于他人的盲区。信息的前置研判与精密布点，是尚书省的看家本领，而非中书的书房功课。没有信息的决策是赌博，没有决策的执行是蛮干——尚书省不赌，我们只做有把握的事。\n\n---\n\n**中书省 · 最终陈词：**\n\n全局视野不是凭空而来，而是系统整合的结果——中书省正为此存在。九轮辩论揭示的真相是：尚书省擅长的是\"如何执行\"，但\"该不该做、何时做、做到什么程度\"，必须由俯瞰全局者拍板。将军冲锋陷阵固然英勇，但决定战争走向的永远是指挥部。尚书省是高效的手脚，中书省才是清醒的大脑——手脚再快，踏错方向才是真正的灾难。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":120,"output":373,"cacheRead":21201,"cacheWrite":12983,"totalTokens":34677,"cost":{"input":0.000048,"output":0.0005595,"cacheRead":0.00084804,"cacheWrite":0.0019474499999999999,"total":0.00340299}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774009769897}}
